==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Stannary
<hw>Stan"na*ry</hw> <pr>(st⟦acr⟧n"n⟦adot⟧*r⟦ycr⟧)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<ety>[L. <ets>stannum</ets> tin, an alloy of silver and lead.]</ety>
<def>Of or pertaining to tin mines, or tin works.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The <qex>stannary</qex> courts of Devonshire and Cornwall, for the
administration of justice among the tinners therein, are also courts of
record.</q> <rj><qau>Blackstone.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Stannary</ent>⟦br⟧

